festival.introText: A hardcore, punk rock music festival in Manchester, UK.

faqs.question: When is Outbreak Fest 2023?
faqs.answer: Outbreak Fest takes place on Friday 23rd June - Sunday 25th June 2023.

faqs.question: Where is Outbreak Fest?
faqs.answer: Outbreak Fest is located at Depot Mayfield, Temperance St, Manchester M12 6HR.

faqs.question: Does Outbreak Fest have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer: Yes, Outbreak Fest is a 14+ event. Anyone under 18 may require an adult to attend with them. Photo ID may be required.
